			<div class="content">This is a great solution for me, thanks. The app I'm running outputs log messages to the console, so I often just plug in a HDMI screen to see the status of the application on the RPi, but I don't connect a keyboard to it.<br /><br />I just set those two lines to 0 (BLANK_TIME and POWERDOWN_TIME) and this worked great.<br />I am running Debian Wheezy (soft-float).</div>

			

