			<div class="content">For me it worked by editing <span style="font-weight: bold">/etc/X11/xinit/xserverrc</span> and changing<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: <a href="#" onclick="selectCode(this); return false;">Select all</a></dt><dd><code>exec /usr/bin/X -nolisten tcp &quot;$@&quot;<br /></code></dd></dl><br />by<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: <a href="#" onclick="selectCode(this); return false;">Select all</a></dt><dd><code>exec /usr/bin/X -s 0 dpms -nolisten tcp &quot;$@&quot;<br /></code></dd></dl><br /><br />I'm using Raspbian “wheezy” and I start my X session with <span style="font-weight: bold">startx</span>.</div>

			

